Cyberpunk style: A solitary figure stands before a massive holographic mirror in a neon-drenched corporate tower, their reflection split down the middle — one half showing a sluggish, hunched silhouette tangled in glowing red data cables and old circuit boards, the other half lean and dynamic, surrounded by flowing streams of bright cyan energy and sleek neural pathways. The room is filled with floating transparent screens displaying heartbeat monitors and network connection graphs that pulse in sync. Rain streaks down floor-to-ceiling windows behind them, revealing a sprawling megacity skyline. The figure reaches toward their transformed reflection with determination, fingers trailing light particles. Deep purple and electric blue atmosphere with sharp magenta accents. Moody, transformative, visceral.
